\nspacetime parametrise certain lightcone cuts in the asymptotic geometries. We\ninclude an appendix comparing with (A)dS and observe that the de Sitter groups\nhave no homogeneous spaces which could play the r\\^ole that the celestial\nsphere plays in flat space holography.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 19:18:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 4 Feb 2022 09:11:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-09-21"}
