me search time, without loss of accuracy, Manas produces models with\n42.9% to 99.6% fewer number of parameters than Auto-Keras' models. Benchmarked\non GPU, Manas' models train 30.3% to 641.6% faster than Auto-Keras' models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Dec 2021 22:34:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 13 Feb 2022 10:54:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-15"}
