ature\ncoefficient $K_{\\rm sym}^{\\rm star}$ of the neutron stars with different mass\nare analyzed and found to be model dependent. NL3 is the stiffest equation of\nstate endue us with the higher magnitude of surface quantities as compared to\nthe G3 and IU-FSU forces.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 06:12:51 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Apr 2022 03:05:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-21"}
