etter\n1QFA, and induce a result regarding a quantitative relationship between the\nstate number of multi-letter 1QFA and DFA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 7 Dec 2021 15:00:18 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Dec 2021 04:17:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-09"}
